our minds, over our wills, our emotions.

00:34:55.280 --> 00:34:57.670
And Jesus, we apply the blood over every

00:34:57.680 --> 00:35:00.310
area of our life.

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:02.470
And we make much of the blood and

00:35:02.480 --> 00:35:04.550
the blood will make much of us. And we

00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:07.349
plead the blood of Jesus Christ over our

00:35:07.359 --> 00:35:09.589
homes, our houses, over our

00:35:09.599 --> 00:35:12.230
finances, over our marriages. And we

00:35:12.240 --> 00:35:14.310
thank you, Lord, that what you did for

00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:15.790
us on that

00:35:15.790 --> 00:35:15.800
cross—it

00:35:15.800 --> 00:35:18.390
was more than what we could

00:35:18.400 --> 00:35:22.069
dare ask or think. Thank you, Lord. And

00:35:22.079 --> 00:35:23.829
we take this blood right now in the name

00:35:23.839 --> 00:35:27.109
of Jesus.

00:35:27.119 --> 00:35:29.270
Lord, we enter in by the blood of the

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:32.310
Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:35:32.320 --> 00:35:34.790
We enter into your throne room. We enter

00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:37.670
into your throne right now, seated

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:40.870
with you like the eagle. Lord, we don't

00:35:40.880 --> 00:35:43.030
want to be a chicken down there

00:35:43.040 --> 00:35:44.630
scratching around trying to find

00:35:44.640 --> 00:35:46.870
yesterday's worm. We're looking for the

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:49.190
good stuff.

00:35:49.200 --> 00:35:52.230
I don't want to be a chicken. I

00:35:52.240 --> 00:35:54.550
don't want to be a rooster. I

00:35:54.560 --> 00:35:56.950
want to be an

00:35:56.960 --> 00:35:59.750
eagle. And I'm going to be an eagle. And

00:35:59.750 --> 00:35:59.760
I will

00:35:59.760 --> 00:36:02.710
fly like an eagle above all the

00:36:02.720 --> 00:36:05.030
storms. And as the storms of life come

00:36:05.040 --> 00:36:08.630
in, we go higher above the storm

00:36:08.640 --> 00:36:11.510
clouds. And we

00:36:11.520 --> 00:36:12.870
don't just stay on the ground and let

00:36:12.880 --> 00:36:14.870
the storm eat us up.

00:36:16.760 --> 00:36:20.550
Father, I thank you, Lord, because

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:22.150
God, you've called us to be more than

00:36:22.160 --> 00:36:24.470
conquerors.

00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:27.430
You called us to be more for such a time

00:36:27.440 --> 00:36:28.670
as this.

00:36:28.680 --> 00:36:32.230
Father, we plead the blood of Jesus over

00:36:32.240 --> 00:36:34.710
our homes, over our marriage, over

00:36:34.720 --> 00:36:37.430
our children, over their

00:36:37.440 --> 00:36:40.069
schools, over everything they do.

00:36:40.079 --> 00:36:42.550
Father, we plead the blood of Jesus over

00:36:42.560 --> 00:36:44.710
our unsaved loved ones, and we call them

00:36:44.720 --> 00:36:47.190
in. For you said you were leaving the

00:36:47.190 --> 00:36:47.200
ninety-nine

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:48.910
and going after the

00:36:48.920 --> 00:36:51.750
one. We thank you Lord for the blood of

00:36:51.760 --> 00:36:53.829
Jesus Christ that we apply over our

00:36:53.839 --> 00:36:56.390
churches. We apply the blood over our

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:59.430
pastors and over our lay pastors,

00:36:59.440 --> 00:37:01.510
Father. We call them strong, Father, in

00:37:01.510 --> 00:37:01.520
these

00:37:01.520 --> 00:37:03.750
end times, that they would

00:37:03.760 --> 00:37:06.870
get great revelation from you to

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:10.870
impart into the body.

00:37:10.880 --> 00:37:12.310
Thank you, Father, that you're raising

00:37:12.320 --> 00:37:15.710
up new men and women of God to take the

00:37:15.720 --> 00:37:18.910
baton, to run the race, and to finish this

00:37:18.920 --> 00:37:21.430
race. Father, we're not just barely

00:37:21.440 --> 00:37:23.670
getting by, but we are finishing the

00:37:23.680 --> 00:37:26.710
race with great

00:37:26.710 --> 00:37:26.720
victory—sweatless

00:37:26.720 --> 00:37:28.870
victory. I'm believing for sweatless

00:37:28.880 --> 00:37:30.630
victory. You said, "Brandon, these are

00:37:30.640 --> 00:37:33.589
days of fun coming."Days of fun. What

00:37:33.599 --> 00:37:35.589
does that look like? Days of fun to the

00:37:35.599 --> 00:37:39.109
Lord is a great harvest. Fun to

00:37:39.119 --> 00:37:40.510
me is seeing God

00:37:40.520 --> 00:37:43.589
happy. What's on God's heart today? What

00:37:43.599 --> 00:37:47.030
makes you happy, Father? Your children,

00:37:47.040 --> 00:37:50.470
a great victory, going from victory to

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:57.470
victory, going from glory to

00:37:57.480 --> 00:38:02.390
glory. Lord, we worship you. We expect

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:06.390
a miracle. We expect to see

00:38:06.400 --> 00:38:09.270
change in our life

00:38:09.270 --> 00:38:09.280
and

00:38:09.280 --> 00:38:11.349
in our government. And Father, as

00:38:11.359 --> 00:38:14.310
we hear about all the things this

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:16.310
week—the

00:38:16.320 --> 00:38:19.030
economy, the stock market, all

00:38:19.040 --> 00:38:21.109
the shaking to

00:38:21.119 --> 00:38:23.589
awaken, the warnings, and

00:38:23.599 --> 00:38:25.910
the signs that you've warned us about

00:38:25.920 --> 00:38:30.510
and screamed from your very

00:38:30.510 --> 00:38:30.520
significance—I

00:38:30.520 --> 00:38:33.430
mean the moon and

00:38:33.440 --> 00:38:38.470
all the elements to speak to us.

00:38:38.480 --> 00:38:40.150
You said you'd give it to us, Father, to

00:38:40.160 --> 00:38:43.390
speak to us. Are we

00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:45.950
listening?

00:38:45.960 --> 00:38:50.670
Signs in the heavens—are we

00:38:50.680 --> 00:38:53.510
listening? Help us, God, not to be so

00:38:53.520 --> 00:38:55.829
complacent and weary in well-doing and

00:38:55.839 --> 00:38:58.310
become so desensitized that we forget

00:38:58.320 --> 00:38:59.910
about something that happened a year ago

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:02.550
and say, "Well, it was a year ago; it means

00:39:02.550 --> 00:39:02.560
nothing,"because

00:39:02.560 --> 00:39:05.349
you are a vast

00:39:05.359 --> 00:39:08.150
God that speaks way bigger than even a

00:39:08.160 --> 00:39:09.390
year

00:39:09.400 --> 00:39:12.030
ago. You're not moved by our little

00:39:12.040 --> 00:39:14.030
timetable; you're moved by your

00:39:14.040 --> 00:39:16.310
timetable. And you're not going, "Well,

00:39:16.320 --> 00:39:17.990
because I didn't do it in that

00:39:18.000 --> 00:39:21.710
first hour, that means it was a

00:39:21.710 --> 00:39:21.720
flop."No,

00:39:21.720 --> 00:39:23.910
you're not moved by our little

00:39:23.920 --> 00:39:25.910
time. Even if it was ten years from now,

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:29.109
it wouldn't mean anything to you. But God, I

00:39:29.119 --> 00:39:31.030
know you're the God who speaks through

00:39:31.040 --> 00:39:34.150
our

00:39:35.760 --> 00:39:38.230
moon and our sun. You speak to

00:39:38.240 --> 00:39:40.390
us through

00:39:40.390 --> 00:39:40.400
eclipses—lunar

00:39:40.400 --> 00:39:42.630
and solar

00:39:42.630 --> 00:39:42.640
eclipses—and

00:39:42.640 --> 00:39:45.829
you show us

00:39:45.839 --> 00:39:48.150
those things that are to come,

00:39:50.119 --> 00:39:52.310
not through astrology;

00:39:52.320 --> 00:39:55.270
astrology is witchcraft. But Father, you

00:39:55.280 --> 00:39:58.109
speak to us like you did

00:39:58.119 --> 00:40:00.950
Daniel.

00:40:03.119 --> 00:40:05.270
Lord, I believe like you did for the

00:40:05.280 --> 00:40:08.030
wise men when they followed the star to

00:40:08.040 --> 00:40:10.710
Bethlehem. They saw the star because

00:40:10.720 --> 00:40:12.750
they knew the King was being

00:40:12.760 --> 00:40:16.950
born. They followed the star

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:20.150
because Jesus was in the star. He

00:40:20.160 --> 00:40:23.109
was coming as a lamb for the

00:40:23.119 --> 00:40:25.270
salvation of us

00:40:25.280 --> 00:40:27.829
all. The wise men knew

00:40:27.839 --> 00:40:30.790
to follow the star; if it wasn't for

00:40:30.800 --> 00:40:32.230
that, they wouldn't have known. But they

00:40:32.240 --> 00:40:34.470
were looking for the sign, and there are

00:40:34.480 --> 00:40:36.310
signs just like there were with the wise

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:38.230
men. There were signs in the heavens,

00:40:38.240 --> 00:40:40.550
and I believe the same God that spoke

00:40:40.560 --> 00:40:43.270
through the star to tell the wise men to

00:40:43.280 --> 00:40:45.150
come is still speaking today. If we're

00:40:45.160 --> 00:40:47.589
listening, you're able to speak to

00:40:47.599 --> 00:40:50.150
us. Father, they say

00:40:50.160 --> 00:40:52.710
there's sign after sign.

00:40:52.720 --> 00:40:54.550
We've already seen a couple years ago the

00:40:54.560 --> 00:40:56.390
sign of Bethlehem. They call it the

00:40:56.400 --> 00:40:58.390
Bethlehem star.

00:40:59.760 --> 00:41:02.270
I believe it was you saying, "I'm coming

00:41:02.270 --> 00:41:02.280
again."You

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:04.950
showed up the first time with

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:07.190
the star, and you are going to show

00:41:07.200 --> 00:41:09.790
up again the second time with the

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:12.030
star. Are we

00:41:12.040 --> 00:41:14.470
listening? Lord, help us to be the ones

00:41:14.470 --> 00:41:14.480
who

00:41:14.480 --> 00:41:17.510
are not so quick to forget the

00:41:17.520 --> 00:41:19.750
signs, even the Bethlehem star that was in

00:41:19.760 --> 00:41:23.270
the sky a couple years ago.

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:26.950
Lord, let us remember and be quick to

00:41:26.960 --> 00:41:29.510
hear it. The stars were so big

00:41:29.520 --> 00:41:31.190
together, Father; it was so bright in

00:41:31.200 --> 00:41:33.790
the sky that everyone would see it

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:37.030
worldwide. The whole world saw that

00:41:37.040 --> 00:41:39.510
major sign in the heavens. People

00:41:39.520 --> 00:41:40.710
are like, "What in the world is

00:41:40.710 --> 00:41:40.720
that?"and

00:41:40.720 --> 00:41:41.990
it's not going to happen again for a long

00:41:42.000 --> 00:41:42.990
time.

00:41:43.000 --> 00:41:46.150
Oh God, help us not to forget

00:41:46.160 --> 00:41:50.069
those signs.

00:41:50.079 --> 00:41:51.870
Lord, I thank

00:41:51.880 --> 00:41:55.270
you that you're good and your mercy

00:41:55.280 --> 00:41:58.230
endures forever. Father,

00:41:58.240 --> 00:42:02.670
you speak to us so loud even in the

00:42:02.680 --> 00:42:05.990
skies. We worship you, Father. We thank

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:07.510
you, Lord, for our president and for Vance. We thank

00:42:07.520 --> 00:42:09.589
you, Lord, for

00:42:09.599 --> 00:42:11.990
the protection over

00:42:11.990 --> 00:42:12.000
them—that

00:42:12.000 --> 00:42:13.670
no weapon formed against them will

00:42:13.680 --> 00:42:15.990
prosper. Every tongue that rises against

00:42:16.000 --> 00:42:17.390
them, we condemn

00:42:17.400 --> 00:42:20.069
it. A curse without a cause cannot

00:42:20.079 --> 00:42:22.230
stand. And we believe, Father, that

00:42:22.240 --> 00:42:24.550
we're not under the curse,

00:42:24.550 --> 00:42:24.560
but

00:42:24.560 --> 00:42:26.150
that we're always in the right place at

00:42:26.160 --> 00:42:29.230
the right time, hearing your

00:42:29.240 --> 00:42:31.829
voice. Lord, we give you praise,

00:42:31.839 --> 00:42:34.470
glory, and honor for the fire of the Holy

00:42:34.480 --> 00:42:36.870
Spirit. As we yield to you, Father,

00:42:36.880 --> 00:42:39.030
we jump in that river right now in the

00:42:39.040 --> 00:42:42.710
name of Jesus

00:42:42.710 --> 00:42:42.720
and

00:42:42.720 --> 00:42:45.510
let the

00:42:45.520 --> 00:42:47.910
Holy Ghost take control. We're

00:42:47.920 --> 00:42:50.150
not just in the lazy

00:42:50.160 --> 00:42:51.589
river all the time, but Father, we're in

00:42:51.599 --> 00:42:54.030
the rapids too—Holy Ghost

00:42:54.040 --> 00:42:56.870
rapids, stirring us up right now in the

00:42:56.880 --> 00:42:59.270
name of Jesus, filled and controlled by

00:42:59.280 --> 00:43:02.630
the Holy Ghost. We thank you, Lord,

00:43:02.640 --> 00:43:04.710
that there are good days ahead for the

00:43:04.720 --> 00:43:06.950
body of Christ as we stay in sync with

00:43:06.960 --> 00:43:09.270
you. But, Father, I know what you said: there

00:43:09.270 --> 00:43:09.280
is

00:43:09.280 --> 00:43:11.589
correction coming in the church. There

00:43:11.599 --> 00:43:13.190
is

00:43:13.200 --> 00:43:14.550
going to be a correction in the

00:43:14.560 --> 00:43:16.870
body. And Father, what more to get their

00:43:16.880 --> 00:43:18.430
attention than their

00:43:18.440 --> 00:43:20.710
pocketbook?

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:25.190
You touch people's wallets

00:43:25.200 --> 00:43:28.510
and they start to say, "Oh, you got my attention."Lord, it's pathetic it has to come to that sometimes, but whatever it takes. Father, I want to be an eagle and I want to soar with you. You've got my

00:43:28.520 --> 00:43:30.630
attention.

00:43:43.760 --> 00:43:46.150
My

00:43:46.160 --> 00:43:49.309
pocketbook is your

00:43:49.319 --> 00:43:52.030
pocketbook. I thank you,

00:43:52.040 --> 00:43:54.430
Father.

00:43:54.440 --> 00:43:57.670
You're the glory and the

00:43:57.680 --> 00:44:00.470
lifter of my head. We are not moved

00:44:00.480 --> 00:44:02.470
by what we see or what

00:44:02.480 --> 00:44:04.390
we feel about this next week or the week

00:44:04.400 --> 00:44:06.710
after.

00:44:06.720 --> 00:44:09.589
We're moved by what you said

00:44:09.589 --> 00:44:09.599
and

00:44:09.599 --> 00:44:11.750
what you've told us we'd

00:44:11.760 --> 00:44:13.270
do,

00:44:13.280 --> 00:44:16.750
and we carry the greater

00:44:16.760 --> 00:44:19.430
works. Lord, we lift up your name. We

00:44:19.440 --> 00:44:22.390
praise you, God. Like you said, you

00:44:22.400 --> 00:44:25.109
are our healer. We call for deliverance

00:44:25.109 --> 00:44:25.119
and

00:44:25.119 --> 00:44:30.829
the restoration of all

00:44:30.839 --> 00:44:39.230
things. Glory to God!

00:44:39.240 --> 00:45:18.800
Hallelujah.

00:45:32.520 --> 00:45:36.309
We stir

00:45:36.309 --> 00:45:36.319
ourselves

00:45:36.319 --> 00:45:39.190
up. We go deeper in the

00:45:39.190 --> 00:45:39.200
wells—the

00:45:39.200 --> 00:45:41.829
great rivers of

00:45:41.839 --> 00:45:44.230
living water that flow out of the inside

00:45:44.240 --> 00:45:47.349
of us. We call forth that river

00:45:47.359 --> 00:45:49.990
to flow on a

00:45:52.319 --> 00:45:54.470
greater level, to go up higher.

00:46:31.760 --> 00:46:34.390
We dance.

00:46:37.920 --> 00:46:40.150
You lead, we follow.

00:46:40.160 --> 00:46:42.950
Your agenda, not ours.

00:46:42.960 --> 00:46:47.030
Oh

00:46:47.040 --> 00:47:10.309
man,

00:47:10.319 --> 00:47:19.030
I see South Korea.

00:47:19.040 --> 00:47:22.309
I see it on the border of North Korea

00:47:22.319 --> 00:47:25.670
and South Korea. I see

00:47:25.680 --> 00:47:28.829
an

00:47:28.839 --> 00:47:33.030
explosion and fire. I see

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:34.790
almost like what you'd see when it

00:47:34.790 --> 00:47:34.800
says

00:47:34.800 --> 00:47:38.550
TNT across it, and I see the fire coming

00:47:38.560 --> 00:47:40.790
out of it.

00:47:40.800 --> 00:47:43.190
It's like a bomb went off on the border

00:47:43.200 --> 00:47:45.750
of South Korea and North Korea,

00:47:45.760 --> 00:47:49.670
on the far west side.

00:47:49.680 --> 00:47:52.470
Not all

00:47:52.480 --> 00:47:55.430
the way out into the ocean, but right

00:47:55.440 --> 00:48:03.309
there. I see some kind of disturbance

00:48:03.319 --> 00:48:25.530
there.

00:48:37.750 --> 00:48:37.760
It

00:48:52.200 --> 00:49:08.390
surely

00:49:08.400 --> 00:49:11.700
is a

00:49:22.200 --> 00:49:25.150
disturbance. They

00:49:25.150 --> 00:49:25.160
are

00:49:25.160 --> 00:49:28.950
trying to break out war there.

00:49:28.960 --> 00:49:32.430
I now see

00:49:32.440 --> 00:49:35.069
China

00:49:35.079 --> 00:49:37.630
provoking. It is like a

00:49:37.640 --> 00:49:41.990
provocation

00:49:42.000 --> 00:49:44.710
with North

00:49:44.720 --> 00:49:47.910
Korea, and China backing North Korea. It

00:49:47.910 --> 00:49:47.920
is

00:49:47.920 --> 00:49:51.430
what I've seen again, with Kim

00:49:51.440 --> 00:49:55.030
Jong-un being backed by China and Russia,

00:49:55.040 --> 00:49:59.390
bringing forth this alliance with

00:49:59.400 --> 00:50:08.760
the

00:50:08.770 --> 00:50:10.829
BRICS

00:50:10.839 --> 00:50:27.660
there. There I go again,

00:50:27.660 --> 00:50:27.670
South

00:50:27.670 --> 00:50:39.309
Korea.

00:50:39.319 --> 00:50:41.670
Why would North

00:50:41.680 --> 00:50:47.470
Korea want a war with South

00:50:47.480 --> 00:50:49.910
Korea? What is that all about?

00:50:49.910 --> 00:50:49.920
It

00:50:49.920 --> 00:50:58.910
is

00:50:58.920 --> 00:51:03.570
about China.

00:51:09.520 --> 00:51:12.870
I see China trying to rise up like a

00:51:12.880 --> 00:51:17.549
great

00:51:17.559 --> 00:51:20.630
dragon in the days

00:51:20.640 --> 00:51:21.950
ahead. You'll see

00:51:21.960 --> 00:51:24.549
movement in the days ahead. Now, I'm not

00:51:24.559 --> 00:51:27.030
saying when. I see

00:51:27.040 --> 00:51:30.630
a movement: China coming

00:51:30.640 --> 00:51:33.109
up like out of a

00:51:33.119 --> 00:51:34.790
volcano.

00:51:34.800 --> 00:51:43.050
I see a red dragon coming up out of

00:51:43.060 --> 00:51:48.670
a

00:51:48.680 --> 00:51:51.750
volcano; it is a fierce dragon. I see fire

00:51:51.760 --> 00:51:56.430
coming from the dragon's

00:51:56.440 --> 00:51:59.670
mouth, and it's flaming toward

00:51:59.680 --> 00:52:02.430
South Korea.

00:52:33.280 --> 00:52:51.670
Now I see Japan again.

00:52:51.670 --> 00:52:51.680
They

00:52:51.680 --> 00:52:53.870
are

00:52:53.880 --> 00:52:56.790
being promised a lot. North

00:52:56.800 --> 00:52:58.549
Korea and Kim Jong-un are being

00:52:58.549 --> 00:52:58.559
promised

00:52:58.559 --> 00:53:01.710
a lot, and it makes them

00:53:01.720 --> 00:53:04.230
confident. There are secret meetings.

00:53:04.230 --> 00:53:04.240
You

00:53:04.240 --> 00:53:07.589
will

00:53:07.599 --> 00:53:24.870
see

00:53:24.880 --> 00:53:27.390
it; it's like what I see about North

00:53:27.400 --> 00:53:34.030
Korea, China, and Russia becoming

00:53:34.040 --> 00:53:36.670
one. I see

00:53:36.680 --> 00:53:40.589
Iran and an alliance of these

00:53:40.599 --> 00:53:45.470
countries, almost

00:53:45.480 --> 00:53:49.950
like they are thinking

00:53:49.950 --> 00:53:49.960
as

00:53:49.960 --> 00:53:52.990
one, like a

00:53:53.000 --> 00:53:56.069
covenant. I

00:53:56.069 --> 00:53:56.079
was

00:53:56.079 --> 00:53:58.190
looking

00:53:58.190 --> 00:53:58.200
at

00:53:58.200 --> 00:54:00.870
Venezuela, and I see Venezuela being

00:54:00.880 --> 00:54:03.910
promised things. Now I'm in Cuba,

00:54:03.920 --> 00:54:06.710
and I see Cuba being promised things.

00:54:06.720 --> 00:54:10.390
I see alliances of Cuba, Venezuela, and

00:54:10.400 --> 00:54:13.109
the countries that have been

00:54:13.109 --> 00:54:13.119
outcasts,

00:54:13.119 --> 00:54:18.510
like

00:54:20.119 --> 00:54:22.330
Afghanistan.

00:54:22.330 --> 00:54:22.340
There

00:54:22.340 --> 00:54:29.230
are

00:54:29.240 --> 00:54:31.589
minerals

00:54:31.589 --> 00:54:31.599
in

00:54:31.599 --> 00:54:34.030
Afghanistan—something

00:54:34.030 --> 00:54:34.040
of

00:54:34.040 --> 00:54:46.270
value

00:54:46.280 --> 00:54:59.349
there. I see Taiwan.

00:54:59.359 --> 00:55:03.290
South Korea and

00:55:07.960 --> 00:55:10.390
Taiwan are allies of

00:55:10.400 --> 00:55:12.390
America, but China

00:55:12.400 --> 00:55:16.549
wants

00:55:38.109 --> 00:55:38.119
them.

00:55:55.280 --> 00:55:56.950
What's interesting is what

00:55:56.960 --> 00:55:59.990
I'm hearing: people only look at what

00:56:00.000 --> 00:56:02.789
they see in the current year.

00:56:02.799 --> 00:56:04.549
They don't believe what

00:56:04.559 --> 00:56:05.990
we believe about the Bible

00:56:05.990 --> 00:56:06.000
or

00:56:06.000 --> 00:56:07.870
the end

00:56:07.880 --> 00:56:11.549
times. They're looking at 50-year

00:56:11.549 --> 00:56:11.559
and

00:56:11.559 --> 00:56:14.030
10-year

00:56:14.030 --> 00:56:14.040
projections.

00:56:14.040 --> 00:56:16.870
What will we be in the next

00:56:16.870 --> 00:56:16.880
several

00:56:16.880 --> 00:56:18.710
decades? How do we get this

00:56:18.720 --> 00:56:21.789
land?

00:56:21.799 --> 00:56:25.990
Like a united

00:56:26.000 --> 00:56:29.349
communism over South Korea, causing

00:56:29.359 --> 00:56:32.349
war. I saw an explosion on the

00:56:32.359 --> 00:56:36.150
border, and I saw

00:56:36.160 --> 00:56:38.230
South Korea unable to

00:56:38.230 --> 00:56:38.240
retaliate. China was

00:56:38.240 --> 00:56:40.950
backing up North Korea,

00:56:40.960 --> 00:56:43.270
coming to their aid. It

00:56:43.270 --> 00:56:43.280
was

00:56:43.280 --> 00:56:45.030
a

00:56:45.040 --> 00:56:48.430
joint

00:56:48.430 --> 00:56:48.440
effort

00:56:48.440 --> 00:56:51.670
to make

00:56:51.670 --> 00:56:51.680
themselves

00:56:51.680 --> 00:56:54.390
greater, similar to Trump

00:56:54.390 --> 00:56:54.400
mentioning

00:56:54.400 --> 00:56:55.990
Greenland

00:56:55.990 --> 00:56:56.000
or

00:56:56.000 --> 00:56:58.630
Canada becoming one with

00:56:58.640 --> 00:57:01.950
America. These are land

00:57:01.960 --> 00:57:04.030
grabs.

00:57:04.030 --> 00:57:04.040
They

00:57:04.040 --> 00:57:07.670
are

00:57:07.670 --> 00:57:07.680
looking

00:57:07.680 --> 00:57:09.870
forward

00:57:09.870 --> 00:57:09.880
to

00:57:09.880 --> 00:57:13.670
what the new world would be, not the

00:57:13.680 --> 00:57:15.910
way the world is right now. Russia

00:57:15.910 --> 00:57:15.920
wants

00:57:15.920 --> 00:57:18.589
the old Soviet

00:57:18.589 --> 00:57:18.599
Union—Ukraine

00:57:18.599 --> 00:57:22.349
and

00:57:22.349 --> 00:57:22.359
Poland—wanting

00:57:22.359 --> 00:57:24.870
that old land back to

00:57:24.870 --> 00:57:24.880
form

00:57:24.880 --> 00:57:27.390
a new, stronger Soviet

00:57:27.400 --> 00:57:39.309
Union with the old KGB

00:57:39.319 --> 00:57:41.750
thinking, playing this game

00:57:41.750 --> 00:57:41.760
like

00:57:41.760 --> 00:57:47.030
chess,

00:57:47.040 --> 00:57:50.510
all lining up with the

00:57:50.510 --> 00:57:50.520
NWO

00:57:50.520 --> 00:57:54.069
system. These people are

00:57:54.079 --> 00:57:55.789
led by their own

00:57:55.799 --> 00:57:59.230
egos, trying to make their nations

00:57:59.230 --> 00:57:59.240
great

00:57:59.240 --> 00:58:01.910
because the tariffs

00:58:01.910 --> 00:58:01.920
are

00:58:01.920 --> 00:58:03.870
tipping them

00:58:03.880 --> 00:58:07.829
off.

00:58:07.839 --> 00:58:10.309
I saw people moving strategically.

00:58:39.119 --> 00:58:41.589
Cuba

00:58:41.589 --> 00:58:41.599
is

00:58:41.599 --> 00:58:44.390
lining up with Russia.

00:58:46.319 --> 00:58:49.750
I see it

00:58:49.750 --> 00:58:49.760
coming—bringing

00:58:49.760 --> 00:58:51.670
them out of

00:58:51.680 --> 00:58:53.990
that. There would be a base down

00:58:54.000 --> 00:58:56.430
there, so strong and close to

00:58:56.440 --> 00:58:59.950
America. That's very

00:58:59.960 --> 00:59:09.069
dangerous. I see

00:59:09.079 --> 00:59:12.630
it like it was with Greenland,

00:59:12.640 --> 00:59:20.510
a strategic move like the game Risk,

00:59:23.599 --> 00:59:25.990
with the spirit of war. It is the Red

00:59:26.000 --> 00:59:27.510
Horse. I

00:59:27.510 --> 00:59:27.520
saw

00:59:27.520 --> 00:59:30.390
the Red Horse

00:59:30.400 --> 00:59:32.789
when I looked at my wife's face;

00:59:32.789 --> 00:59:32.799
it

00:59:32.799 --> 00:59:35.390
was riding

00:59:35.400 --> 00:59:39.109
quickly. The Red Horse of war is riding

00:59:39.119 --> 00:59:42.870
quickly. Therefore,

00:59:42.880 --> 00:59:45.390
on the heels of this

00:59:45.400 --> 00:59:48.870
horse, the green

00:59:48.870 --> 00:59:48.880
horse—the

00:59:48.880 --> 00:59:51.030
chlorophyll horse—and the black horse

00:59:51.040 --> 00:59:54.990
will ride hand in hand

00:59:55.000 --> 00:59:58.390
together, for famine and pestilence will

00:59:58.400 --> 01:00:04.349
go hand in hand.

01:00:04.359 --> 01:00:23.390
War, war, war.

01:01:10.240 --> 01:01:29.510
Everything is going to change.

01:01:29.520 --> 01:01:59.109
I say it again:

01:01:59.119 --> 01:02:00.630
I don't know if I'm looking into the

01:02:00.640 --> 01:02:12.200
Tribulation or not.

01:02:16.160 --> 01:02:48.230
I went so far ahead;

01:02:48.240 --> 01:02:50.750
surely that's

01:02:50.750 --> 01:02:50.760
the

01:02:50.760 --> 01:03:19.630
Tribulation.

01:03:19.640 --> 01:03:24.109
Oh, the great Mystery

01:03:24.119 --> 01:03:44.510
Babylon.

01:04:23.520 --> 01:04:27.190
I see a massive volcano going off

01:04:27.200 --> 01:04:31.430
in

01:04:31.440 --> 01:04:34.309
Asia; it

01:04:34.319 --> 01:04:37.270
looks like it could be Japan or those

01:04:37.280 --> 01:04:38.750
islands right

01:04:38.760 --> 01:04:42.270
there.

01:04:42.280 --> 01:04:44.950
It

01:04:44.960 --> 01:04:46.670
is a massive

01:04:46.680 --> 01:04:51.710
volcano, big

01:04:51.710 --> 01:04:51.720
enough

01:04:51.720 --> 01:04:55.109
to change the

01:04:55.119 --> 01:04:57.990
face of the earth.

01:04:58.000 --> 01:05:02.549
I see

01:05:02.559 --> 01:05:14.430
lava flowing down the side of this

01:05:14.440 --> 01:05:23.029
mountain. I

01:05:23.039 --> 01:05:39.710
think I'm looking into the

01:05:39.720 --> 01:05:52.789
Tribulation.

01:08:11.400 --> 01:08:14.870
Now I'll tell you

01:08:14.880 --> 01:08:17.349
what

01:08:19.480 --> 01:08:31.030
I'm looking at: Canada.

01:08:31.040 --> 01:08:33.749
Then it went from Canada all

01:08:33.759 --> 01:08:36.149
the way to the royals in England. I

01:08:36.149 --> 01:08:36.159
saw

01:08:36.159 --> 01:08:53.740
King Charles.

01:08:58.400 --> 01:09:00.149
Then it

01:09:00.159 --> 01:09:13.110
barely influenced Australia.

01:09:13.120 --> 01:09:22.590
Canada, England,

01:09:22.590 --> 01:09:22.600
and

01:09:22.600 --> 01:09:25.550
Australia with the King of

01:09:25.560 --> 01:09:29.749
England.

01:09:29.759 --> 01:09:34.910
Now I'm in

01:09:34.920 --> 01:09:53.380
Ireland.

01:10:08.159 --> 01:10:44.080
It's like a scorpion.

01:12:55.600 --> 01:12:57.229
Father, I thank

01:12:57.239 --> 01:13:00.669
you.

01:14:22.679 --> 01:14:25.350
I don't even know how to

01:14:25.360 --> 01:14:33.910
describe it with words;

01:14:33.920 --> 01:15:08.709
my vocabulary is not

01:15:08.719 --> 01:15:33.430
sufficient.

01:15:33.440 --> 01:15:36.830
It's past the

01:15:36.840 --> 01:15:51.350
Tribulation; I saw past the Tribulation

01:15:51.360 --> 01:16:31.110
with a New Heaven and a New Earth.

01:16:31.120 --> 01:16:32.950
Some things you just can't say

01:16:32.960 --> 01:16:36.910
out

01:16:36.920 --> 01:16:39.830
loud. I can't

01:17:43.679 --> 01:17:46.350
even give it words in English.

01:17:55.800 --> 01:17:58.709
It looks like

01:17:58.719 --> 01:18:00.950
beautiful yellows and all

01:18:00.960 --> 01:18:04.350
kinds of

01:18:04.360 --> 01:18:08.669
colors, almost like a

01:18:08.679 --> 01:18:14.630
galaxy.

01:18:14.640 --> 01:18:16.030
I saw new

01:18:16.040 --> 01:18:21.550
grass and new land

01:18:21.560 --> 01:18:24.070
features. I saw the people coming out of what

01:18:24.070 --> 01:18:24.080
looked

01:18:24.080 --> 01:18:26.070
like

01:18:26.070 --> 01:18:26.080
a

01:18:26.080 --> 01:18:28.830
fraidy

01:18:28.840 --> 01:18:31.350
hole. The people come up

01:18:31.360 --> 01:18:32.750
in this new

01:18:32.760 --> 01:18:36.630
land, and it was green,

01:18:39.120 --> 01:18:41.390
like the Garden of Eden all over

01:18:41.400 --> 01:18:43.790
again. Everything was

01:18:43.800 --> 01:18:46.470
alive. The trees

01:18:46.470 --> 01:18:46.480
were

01:18:46.480 --> 01:18:47.669
like what I've

01:18:47.679 --> 01:18:49.709
seen of the Garden of

01:18:49.719 --> 01:18:57.870
Eden. Everything was

01:18:57.880 --> 01:18:59.630
new. There

01:18:59.630 --> 01:18:59.640
was

01:18:59.640 --> 01:19:02.669
no

01:19:02.679 --> 01:19:05.470
pollution;

01:19:14.320 --> 01:19:18.669
all of it was brand

01:19:18.679 --> 01:19:21.590
new and happened in a moment.

01:19:22.840 --> 01:19:27.390
It came out of the

01:19:27.400 --> 01:19:30.630
Spirit and transformed everything

01:19:30.630 --> 01:19:30.640
with

01:19:30.640 --> 01:19:35.070
just a word.

01:19:42.120 --> 01:19:44.630
He said, 'Behold, I make all

01:19:44.640 --> 01:19:46.110
things

01:19:46.120 --> 01:19:48.790
new.'The

01:19:48.800 --> 01:19:51.510
fields were fresh,

01:19:51.520 --> 01:19:52.990
and

01:19:53.000 --> 01:19:56.669
the sky was full of light

01:19:56.669 --> 01:19:56.679
with

01:19:56.679 --> 01:19:59.189
no darkness.

01:19:59.199 --> 01:20:02.149
The canopy

01:20:02.159 --> 01:20:04.070
above the earth—the

01:20:04.070 --> 01:20:04.080
atmosphere—looked

01:20:04.080 --> 01:20:09.070
like beautiful

01:20:09.080 --> 01:20:13.229
colors. I saw pinks and

01:20:13.239 --> 01:20:15.990
yellows.

01:20:28.679 --> 01:20:31.030
Everything changed

01:20:31.040 --> 01:20:33.750
instantaneously.

01:20:35.920 --> 01:20:37.830
I was looking in, and

01:20:37.840 --> 01:20:39.430
it was moving like a movie

01:20:39.440 --> 01:20:41.510
screen. Everything was coming so fast.

01:20:43.600 --> 01:20:45.669
I could see wars

01:20:45.669 --> 01:20:45.679
and

01:20:45.679 --> 01:20:48.229
plans, and all of a

01:20:48.239 --> 01:20:52.430
sudden, humanity

01:20:52.440 --> 01:20:54.950
stopped. Everything

01:20:54.960 --> 01:20:57.149
was made

01:20:57.159 --> 01:21:00.470
new. We,

01:21:00.470 --> 01:21:00.480
the

01:21:00.480 --> 01:21:04.630
Body—the

01:21:04.630 --> 01:21:04.640
Bride—were

01:21:04.640 --> 01:21:07.669
here. Everything was fresh,

01:21:07.679 --> 01:21:11.630
like a New Heaven and a New Earth.

01:21:14.679 --> 01:21:16.870
Everything we have ever

01:21:16.880 --> 01:21:21.229
known is about to

01:21:21.239 --> 01:21:23.709
change for that thousand-year reign. I saw a

01:21:23.709 --> 01:21:23.719
glimpse of it

01:21:23.719 --> 01:21:26.390
again.

01:21:26.390 --> 01:21:26.400
It

01:21:26.400 --> 01:21:28.350
doesn't

01:21:28.360 --> 01:21:30.790
happen very often, but I

01:21:30.800 --> 01:21:32.790
want to camp there.

01:21:32.800 --> 01:21:37.669
When I try to describe it in words, I can't. It

01:21:37.669 --> 01:21:37.679
is

01:21:37.679 --> 01:21:45.030
beautiful.

01:21:45.040 --> 01:21:56.629
I feel His fire all over me.

01:21:56.639 --> 01:22:00.350
Oh, what He has so much in store for

01:22:00.360 --> 01:22:08.990
us for a thousand

01:22:09.000 --> 01:22:11.350
years. People better get excited about

01:22:11.360 --> 01:22:18.550
it.

01:22:18.560 --> 01:22:22.390
I can't explain to you how green

01:22:22.400 --> 01:22:24.350
everything

01:22:24.360 --> 01:22:27.350
was. The grass, the trees, and the

01:22:27.350 --> 01:22:27.360
bushes—there

01:22:27.360 --> 01:22:30.830
was no

01:22:30.840 --> 01:22:32.950
death. There was no death. You

01:22:32.960 --> 01:22:34.390
know how you see a dead limb here and

01:22:34.400 --> 01:22:36.790
there? Outside, you go outside

01:22:36.790 --> 01:22:36.800
and

01:22:36.800 --> 01:22:39.270
there's a dead tree limb. There was no

01:22:39.280 --> 01:22:42.629
death. There

01:22:42.629 --> 01:22:42.639
were

01:22:42.639 --> 01:22:46.709
no dead brown leaves. Everything

01:22:46.719 --> 01:22:50.830
is alive and

01:22:50.840 --> 01:22:54.910
green. The sky is

01:22:54.920 --> 01:23:00.669
alive. The very atmosphere is

01:23:00.679 --> 01:23:05.270
alive. And even the grass was

01:23:05.280 --> 01:23:09.430
perfect. It was green, but it's thick,

01:23:09.440 --> 01:23:11.390
almost like you see that old Easter

01:23:11.400 --> 01:23:14.070
basket grass. I don't know

01:23:14.080 --> 01:23:15.430
how else to describe it to you.

01:23:15.440 --> 01:23:20.110
Like you'd see

01:23:20.120 --> 01:23:22.510
moss on

01:23:22.520 --> 01:23:25.430
trees, it's so thick,

01:23:25.440 --> 01:23:27.270
like you could breathe it in, eat

01:23:27.280 --> 01:23:30.910
it, or drink it like the

01:23:30.920 --> 01:23:36.390
grass. Everything is so alive.

01:23:36.400 --> 01:23:38.310
I could just look into it, but I was

01:23:38.310 --> 01:23:38.320
pulled

01:23:38.320 --> 01:23:40.550
back and I looked over here

01:23:40.560 --> 01:23:42.390
and I could see it. As far as I

01:23:42.400 --> 01:23:44.430
could see, it was

01:23:44.440 --> 01:23:47.110
new and beautiful

01:23:47.110 --> 01:23:47.120
with

01:23:47.120 --> 01:23:50.550
pinks and yellows, and the sky was so

01:23:50.560 --> 01:23:53.350
alive.

01:23:53.360 --> 01:23:57.149
It happened as a swirl above the

01:23:57.159 --> 01:24:00.390
atmosphere, like a portal

01:24:00.400 --> 01:24:02.950
opened up. All of a sudden this

01:24:02.960 --> 01:24:05.510
portal was turning, and all of a sudden all

01:24:05.510 --> 01:24:05.520
this newness

01:24:05.520 --> 01:24:08.470
just came out of it and

01:24:08.480 --> 01:24:11.070
it just transferred

01:24:11.080 --> 01:24:13.510
everything. The portal was

01:24:13.510 --> 01:24:13.520
open

01:24:13.520 --> 01:24:15.669
and I could see it was

01:24:15.679 --> 01:24:17.950
like the size of a galaxy. It was

01:24:17.960 --> 01:24:20.390
massive. All of a sudden I saw this

01:24:20.400 --> 01:24:23.510
blue dot that looked like an Earth.

01:24:23.520 --> 01:24:25.189
It came out of it, and I thought it

01:24:25.199 --> 01:24:26.110
was an atom—like an

01:24:26.120 --> 01:24:29.870
atom

01:24:29.870 --> 01:24:29.880
or

01:24:29.880 --> 01:24:31.830
particles. That's what I thought I was

01:24:31.840 --> 01:24:48.990
looking at. But it was something

01:24:49.000 --> 01:24:51.990
new. As I was praying to the King and

01:24:52.000 --> 01:24:53.870
all these other

01:24:53.880 --> 01:24:57.470
things, I could see a scorpion's

01:24:57.480 --> 01:25:01.070
tail; I saw a scorpion. It was a part of

01:25:01.080 --> 01:25:03.430
that. All of a sudden, I kept going

01:25:03.440 --> 01:25:04.629
and going, like I was going

01:25:04.639 --> 01:25:06.550
faster and faster. I could see the

01:25:06.560 --> 01:25:10.149
King of England, and I could see

01:25:10.159 --> 01:25:12.390
there was so much demonic attached to

01:25:12.400 --> 01:25:14.790
that with the Illuminati and things

01:25:14.800 --> 01:25:16.229
like that. I was in the spirit and I

01:25:16.239 --> 01:25:18.310
could see it, and it was pulling me.

01:25:18.320 --> 01:25:20.790
I could see all the darkness in Europe.

01:25:20.800 --> 01:25:22.070
All of a sudden,

01:25:22.080 --> 01:25:23.830
I could see the agendas of

01:25:23.840 --> 01:25:25.510
China and all this stuff going on, and

01:25:25.520 --> 01:25:28.310
the war. I saw a major war

01:25:28.320 --> 01:25:29.709
break out in

01:25:29.719 --> 01:25:31.709
America.

01:25:31.719 --> 01:25:34.790
I pray and hope this is

